name: QuadCorners
documentation: Identifies the four corners of a quadrilateral oriented in a coordinate system such that the origin (0,0) is
both the highest and leftmost point in the system.

topLeftX.documentation: X coordinate of a quadrilateral's upper-left corner.

topLeftY.documentation: Y coordinate of a quadrilateral's upper-left corner.

topRightX.documentation: X coordinate of a quadrilateral's upper-right corner.

topRightY.documentation: Y coordinate of a quadrilateral's upper-right corner.

bottomLeftX.documentation: X coordinate of a quadrilateral's lower-left corner.

bottomLeftY.documentation: Y coordinate of a quadrilateral's lower-left corner.

bottomRightX.documentation: X coordinate of a quadrilateral's lower-right corner.

bottomRightY.documentation: Y coordinate of a quadrilateral's lower-right corner.
